item.title: Heres alittle something i found when mopar was down
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

it's kind of like fscript cause look @ this:

' Script name: Auto Talker
' Author: vKiLLeRv
' Version: 1.0.0.0
' Date: 2/20/2006
' Author Comment: Auto Talker!
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
Text1 = "Enter Text here" 'Enter the text where indicated.
Text2 = "Blue!"           'Parenthecies are required.
Text3 = "RED!"            
Delay = 500               'Delay between messages
NumberToSay = 4 '1 for Text1; 2 for Text2; 3 for Text3; 4 for all
HowManyTimes = 2 'How many times to repeat
'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''
Sub Begin()
Writeln("Auto Talker by vKiLLeRv")
Wait(1000)
MinimizeMe
Wait(2000)
WriteText
Writeln("Finished!")
RestoreMe
End Sub
Sub WriteText()
If NumberToSay = 1 Then
WriteText1
End If
If NumberToSay = 2 Then
WriteText2
End If
If NumberToSay = 3 Then
WriteText3
End If
If NumberToSay = 4 Then
WriteAll
End If
End Sub
Sub WriteText1()
Do Until HowManyTimes = 0
TypeKeys(Text1)
Wait(Delay)
HowManyTimes = HowManyTimes - 1
Loop
End Sub
Sub WriteText2()
Do Until HowManyTimes = 0
TypeKeys(Text2)
Wait(Delay)
HowManyTimes = HowManyTimes - 1
Loop
End Sub
Sub WriteText3()
Do Until HowManyTimes = 0
TypeKeys(Text3)
Wait(Delay)
HowManyTimes = HowManyTimes - 1
Loop
End Sub
Sub WriteAll()
Do Until HowManyTimes = 0
TypeKeys(Text1)
Wait(Delay)
TypeKeys(Text2)
Wait(Delay)
TypeKeys(Text3)
Wait(Delay)
HowManyTimes = HowManyTimes - 1
Loop
End Sub
